---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/privacy.css';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Zumeno Learn">
  <section class="content-section">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: April 19, 2025</p>

    <p>We respect your privacy and take it seriously.</p>

    <h2>What we Collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Basic account information (like email) when you sign up</li>
      <li>Other basic information might be collected for the functionality of the AI tool</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>What we Don't Do</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>We don't sell or share your personal data</li>
      <li>We don't track you across the web</li>
      <li>No third-party ad networks</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Security</h2>
    <p>We take reasonable steps to keep your data safe, but no system is 100% secure. Use strong passwords and don't share them.</p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>This policy may change. You'll be notified if it's something major.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out via the <a href="/contact">Contact</a> page.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>
